  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for the Energy Finance Program&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;This grant will support Climate Policy Initiative&#x2019;s Energy Finance Program in meeting its three goals: (a) the development and propagation of models, tools, and processes to identify and manage climate transition risk; (b) encouraging energy market reform around carbon-free resources; and (c), using finance as a catalyst to implement low-carbon solutions. The Initiative will build on earlier work, on both transition risk and market reform, to identify which types of investors would be encouraged to make carbon-reducing investments; and then research new financial instruments, portfolio designs, or hedging products that could help reduce the risk and lower the financing cost of low-carbon solutions. &quot;</narrative>
  </description>
